{"type": "article", "id": 27729, "title": "一个帮人提高情商的学校，来自作家阿兰·德波顿", "description": "“我相信写作和艺术的最终目的是对人们的生活起治疗作用。”", "date": "2016-06-03T07:00:44Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 31, "name": "英国"}, {"id": 28548, "name": "The School of Life"}, {"id": 1433, "name": "阿兰·德波顿"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 7, "praise_count": 114, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702132721yNmrePZVqK04vT8B.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">          </p>\n<p>英国作家阿兰·德波顿一直想要通过写作以外的事影响世界，我们曾经介绍过他在 2010 年发起的<a href=\"http://www.qdaily.com/articles/25976.html\">“Living Architecture”</a>项目，联合当代建筑师在英国各地修建具有现代设计感且可参观、出租的小屋，来改变英国人对传统建筑的保守态度。这个小屋至今已修建了 7 幢。</p>\n<p>2008 年夏天创立的“人生学校”（<a href=\"http://www.theschooloflife.com/london/\">The School of Life</a>）更能体现阿兰·德波顿的野心，他想要通过文化的作用来帮助人们提高情商。</p>\n<p>事情是这样的：他将伦敦 Marchmont 街道的一处三层的商店改建，一楼举办沙龙，二楼卖书，三楼提供讲座课程，就像是一个书店的综合体，兼具沙龙、商店和教育功能。</p>\n<p>商店部分分为文创产品和书籍，阿兰·德波顿以 The School of Life 为系列推出了一系列彩色的小册子，他拉来了一些心理学家写作，书名多以“how to”为结构，比如“How To Deal with Adversity”“How To Be Alone”“How To Worry Less About Money”。抛开内容不看，单是每本书的封面就很容易吸引年轻人，拥有简洁时尚的美感，适合随身携带或在地铁上翻看，每本书售价 £7.99，目前已出了三个系列共 18 本。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132714xVJyoq9hM4Tt53AI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.74074074\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213271434PCkZHO8JoV6AxU.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51884058\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p class=\"\">文创产品也具有时尚的特征，像沙漏、布袋都显得非常文艺。也有一些提高“情商”的卡片，比如“Know Yourself”卡片通过一些问题让人更好地认识自己。</p>\n<p>目前，The School of Life 商店在阿姆斯特丹、墨尔本、巴黎、安特卫普、伊斯坦布尔、贝尔格莱德（塞尔维亚首都）等地方开店。</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132715oOB95ZIgaTFnqsku.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51884058\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images multiple\">\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132715H4xy6owD38NUtTSV.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132715fwq1O4ilGTnvYeU5.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132716WB9T8bwh4rC2d1kK.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021327161THhuDq89N2cknZS.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132716cw0WEamYJ1bKULgy.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66111111\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132717DY9JzThcWatpQFVw.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132717JtR5uIGvVBYki1Om.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132718Yhl2PIOC9FxXTzeu.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021327187TxMy8UnmzfEgCXr.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132719TLMmEaywnoc9zkW1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702132719eNi8Okw3Tr1d2SZI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.62407407\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"></div>\n<p>课程和活动也围绕着“人生”的主题，题目类似于如何管理压力、谈话的艺术等，也会邀请相应的心理学家开课。此外，他们还举办夏季舞会等活动以吸引年轻人。</p>\n<p>          </p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images\"><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070213272039ESwpquPQaXr0Te.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.51884058\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure></div>\n<p>不过，阿兰·德波顿在英国媒体眼中的评价并不高，包括《卫报》在内的媒体称之为“励志鸡汤写手”，这样看来这个人生学校（The School of Life）也不例外。他说“我相信写作和艺术的最终目的是对人们的生活起治疗作用”，也许你真的能从中获得治愈。<br></p>\n<p class=\"\">图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.theschooloflife.com/london/\">The School of Life</a>、<a href=\"http://www.everydayobject.us/2016/05/30/the-school-of-life/\">everydayobject</a></p>\n\n"}